Dreamgirls;;71;;79;;PG-13;;Deena (Beyoncé Knowles),Effie (Jennifer Hudson) and Lorrell (Anika Noni Rose) form a music trio called the Dreamettes. When ambitious manager Curtis Taylor Jr. (Jamie Foxx) spots the act at a talent show, he offers the chance of a lifetime, to be backup singers for a national star (Eddie Murphy). Taylor takes creative control of the group and eventually pushes the singers into the spotlight. However, one becomes the star, forcing another out, which teaches them about the high cost of fame.;;Musical,Drama;;Bill Condon;;2006;;Jamie Foxx,Beyoncé,Eddie Murphy,Jennifer Hudson,Anika Noni Rose,Keith D. Robinson,Hinton Battle,Sharon Leal,Danny Glover,John Lithgow,Dawnn Lewis,John Krasinski;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dreamgirls